title: [LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan 704 - The Jet-Black Mystery Tra
description:
The four-part thriller finally comes to a close, but not without a huge bang. The train; as well as its passengers, go forth to their final destination?! Will the Black Organization win? What was the motivation behind the locked room murder? Where did Haibara run to? Who is Bourbon? Find out in Detective Conan 704, The Jet-Black Mystery Train (Destination)!
